Come on, take this.

878
00:37:09,950 --> 00:37:11,800
Since we're so similar,
just take this with you.

879
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,390
Thank you.

880
00:37:12,620 --> 00:37:14,180
Don't mention it. We're too similar!

881
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:18,470
Buddy, your gear

882
00:37:18,540 --> 00:37:19,990
is quite a mix.

883
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:21,620
It's pretty nice.

884
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:23,140
Listen, Jing,

885
00:37:23,430 --> 00:37:24,470
as guys,

886
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:25,680
we need to be delicate too.

887
00:37:25,750 --> 00:37:26,990
I think you also

888
00:37:27,060 --> 00:37:27,950
have a good base too.

889
00:37:28,340 --> 00:37:29,540
But, you shouldn't slack off.

890
00:37:29,540 --> 00:37:31,660
Or you won't be able
to get a girlfriend here either.

891
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:34,100
Thank you.

892
00:37:36,580 --> 00:37:37,350
Wait.

893
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:42,100
You didn't disinfect it.

894
00:37:42,100 --> 00:37:42,580
Are you...

895
00:37:43,100 --> 00:37:44,660
A Virgo?

896
00:37:44,720 --> 00:37:46,780
I'm tough on the outside,
and soft on the inside.

897
00:37:46,830 --> 00:37:48,220
I'm a meticulous person.

898
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:50,910
It's done.

899
00:37:52,220 --> 00:37:53,870
What did you mean just now?

900
00:37:55,620 --> 00:37:57,180
In other words,

901
00:37:57,390 --> 00:37:59,180
I'm a "hidden gem" type of guy

902
00:37:59,180 --> 00:38:00,060
with rich emotions.

903
00:38:01,140 --> 00:38:01,700
Alright.

904
00:38:01,910 --> 00:38:03,310
You, carry on.

905
00:38:03,310 --> 00:38:03,950
Alright.

906
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:08,180
Where is this roommate?

907
00:38:09,350 --> 00:38:10,220
He is Zhang Yang.

908
00:38:10,310 --> 00:38:11,460
He went out to play soccer.

909
00:38:11,470 --> 00:38:12,350
You unpack first.

910
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,140
Come on.

911
00:38:15,870 --> 00:38:16,620
Such a coincidence.

912
00:38:17,390 --> 00:38:18,020
Thanks.

913
00:38:26,390 --> 00:38:27,100
Disinfectant.

914
00:38:27,220 --> 00:38:28,140
Disinfectant.

915
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:30,580
Thanks.

916
00:38:30,660 --> 00:38:31,500
Not a big deal.

917
00:38:49,660 --> 00:38:50,310
Song Cong,

918
00:38:50,750 --> 00:38:51,660
do you know whose bed

919
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,430
is opposite?

920
00:38:53,350 --> 00:38:53,790
Who?

921
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:54,950
Lin Jingyi.

922
00:38:55,100 --> 00:38:56,220
Our school's top scorer.

923
00:38:57,870 --> 00:38:58,790
I really want to see

924
00:38:58,830 --> 00:39:00,060
what kind of person he is

925
00:39:00,270 --> 00:39:01,020
who can obtain

926
00:39:01,020 --> 00:39:02,100
such a crazy high score.

927
00:39:20,140 --> 00:39:20,910
Hello, Song.

928
00:39:21,310 --> 00:39:21,830
What's up?

929
00:39:22,100 --> 00:39:23,540
When are you coming to register?

930
00:39:25,310 --> 00:39:26,990
Oh, I forgot to tell you.

931
00:39:27,180 --> 00:39:28,750
I didn't get into Yenching University.

932
00:39:28,830 --> 00:39:30,420
I'm at Wuan University now.

933
00:39:31,270 --> 00:39:32,790
You applied for a second choice?

934
00:39:33,460 --> 00:39:34,750
Then, why didn't you tell me

935
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:35,960
when I asked you the other day

936
00:39:35,960 --> 00:39:37,260
if you wanted to come with me?

937
00:39:38,750 --> 00:39:40,790
Because I was afraid that if I told you,

938
00:39:40,790 --> 00:39:42,220
you'd tell Aunt Hao,

939
00:39:42,470 --> 00:39:44,830
and then the whole family
housing compound would know.

940
00:39:44,900 --> 00:39:46,480
How would I surprise Chen Huan'er then?

941
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:49,350
Are you sure it's a surprise

942
00:39:49,660 --> 00:39:50,430
and not a shock?

943
00:39:51,470 --> 00:39:52,270
You're right.

944
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,540
It probably was a shock.

945
00:39:54,790 --> 00:39:55,540
She's mad at me.

946
00:39:55,950 --> 00:39:57,830
You're so bad, Jing Xichi.

947
00:39:59,140 --> 00:40:00,940
I suggest you properly apologize to her.

948
00:40:02,140 --> 00:40:02,910
Alright, I got it.

949
00:40:03,310 --> 00:40:03,990
Anything else?

950
00:40:04,100 --> 00:40:05,280
If not, I'm hanging up.

951
00:40:09,390 --> 00:40:10,780
Fighting with your girlfriend?

952
00:40:11,910 --> 00:40:12,470
No.

953
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:14,440
It's just my childhood friend.

954
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:16,470
It's childhood sweethearts then.

955
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:38,270
(Have you finished unpacking?)

956
00:40:38,400 --> 00:40:40,140
(Our dorm doesn't
have air conditioning.)

957
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:41,360
(Do you have one in your dorm?)

958
00:40:41,390 --> 00:40:42,060
(And,)

959
00:40:42,060 --> 00:40:43,880
(what about we have
dinner together tonight?)

960
00:40:44,920 --> 00:40:46,720
Who wants to have dinner with you?

961
00:40:54,660 --> 00:40:55,310
What's this?

962
00:41:03,470 --> 00:41:04,140
(Huan'er,)

963
00:41:04,160 --> 00:41:05,860
(this is a medicine kit
I prepared for you)

964
00:41:05,860 --> 00:41:07,440
(for preventing acclimatization issues.)

965
00:41:07,580 --> 00:41:08,350
(One pack for you,)

966
00:41:08,540 --> 00:41:09,620
(one pack for Xichi.)

967
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:16,020
So, I was the only one who didn't know?

968
00:41:16,020 --> 00:41:17,600
Everyone was keeping this from me?

969
00:41:27,100 --> 00:41:27,910
(I'm Tian Chi.)

970
00:41:27,990 --> 00:41:29,180
(This is my phone number.)

971
00:41:29,310 --> 00:41:30,620
(If you need any help,)

972
00:41:30,680 --> 00:41:31,540
(feel free to ask.)

973
00:41:34,620 --> 00:41:35,830
(Senior Tian Chi,)

974
00:41:36,750 --> 00:41:37,580
(how did you get)

975
00:41:37,580 --> 00:41:38,660
(my phone number?)

976
00:41:41,380 --> 00:41:43,000
(I'm in charge
of freshman registration.)

977
00:41:43,020 --> 00:41:44,200
(Your personal information)

978
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:45,460
(is in the student handbook.)

979
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,140
(Thank you for your help this morning.)

980
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,270
(Don't mention it.)

981
00:42:03,180 --> 00:42:03,900
How bad!

982
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,180
They are too bad!

983
00:42:26,001 --> 00:42:31,171
♪Fallen leaves flutter past your gaze♪

984
00:42:32,961 --> 00:42:38,041
♪I dream of worlds within your days♪

985
00:42:39,811 --> 00:42:45,161
♪Countless times,
I write your name in my heart♪

986
00:42:45,471 --> 00:42:50,961
♪Wishes whispered to the stars above♪

987
00:42:53,551 --> 00:42:58,571
♪How many faces in the glass I see♪

988
00:43:00,361 --> 00:43:05,601
♪Time's gentle hand
pulling me out of my cocoon♪

989
00:43:07,201 --> 00:43:12,621
♪Under the sun,
a rainbow butterfly takes flight♪

990
00:43:13,081 --> 00:43:18,581
♪To rest upon your left shoulder bright♪

991
00:43:19,781 --> 00:43:23,741
♪I still hear your promise in my ears♪

992
00:43:23,741 --> 00:43:28,731
♪Before we said goodbye,
your spirit free♪

993
00:43:28,861 --> 00:43:32,291
♪And full of life♪

994
00:43:33,581 --> 00:43:37,041
♪If summer could last a little longer♪

995
00:43:37,041 --> 00:43:42,151
♪Would regrets rewrite
where we'd gone wrong?♪

996
00:43:42,411 --> 00:43:46,801
♪And let me be there with you
at the end of the story♪

997
00:43:47,301 --> 00:43:51,201
♪Watching your silhouette from behind♪

998
00:43:51,201 --> 00:43:56,141
♪My footsteps slow, we were too young♪

999
00:43:56,141 --> 00:43:58,931
♪To know right from wrong♪

1000
00:44:00,841 --> 00:44:04,371
♪Your sweat-kissed face
I hold in my memory♪

1001
00:44:04,371 --> 00:44:07,621
♪Glows as bright as ever♪

1002
00:44:07,781 --> 00:44:13,541
♪I hope one day we'll meet again♪

1003
00:44:13,961 --> 00:44:18,561
♪At just the right time♪
